    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Copy database to another database through command]]></title>
    <link href="funonrails.com/2010/02/copy-database-to-another-database/"/>
    <updated>2010-02-16T16:53:00+05:30</updated>
    <id>funonrails.com/2010/02/copy-database-to-another-database</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class='post'>
<b>1. Copy One database to another database on same host </b><br/><pre class=ruby> mysqldump -uroot -p <source_database_name> | mysql -uroot <dest_database_name></pre> <b>2. Copy database to another database on remote host</b><br/><pre class=ruby> mysqldump -uroot -p <source_database> | ssh host2 "mysql -uroot <dest_database>" </pre></div>

]]></content>
